ext-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u00a0<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/demogiasu.vntsc.vn\/uploads\/news\/Gia-Su-Cac-Mon\/Sinh-Hoc\/hot_2.gif\" alt=\"\" \/>\u00a0Hotline: 0963.138.511 \u2013 0862.856.500<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_BIEU_HIEN_KHI_CON_CAN_MOT_GIA_SU_VAN_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\">I &#8211; BI\u1ec2U HI\u1ec6N KHI CON C\u1ea6N M\u1ed8T GIA S\u01af V\u0102N T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Con b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t m\u00f4n V\u0103n kh\u00f4ng? Con c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u0103n, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n 8\/10 h\u1ecdc sinh ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng, thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng&#8230;&#8230; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m con s\u1ee3?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0C\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh v\u0103n c\u1ee7a con k\u00e9m, ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n h\u1eb9p?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Con kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea1o c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i v\u0103n ho\u00e0n ch\u1ec9nh. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1edf b\u00e0i, th\u00e2n b\u00e0i, k\u1ebft b\u00e0i?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Con ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o v\u0103n m\u1eabu, l\u00e2u d\u1ea7n s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen x\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Con kh\u00f4ng theo k\u1ecbp b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 tr\u00ean l\u1edbp?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0Con c\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c trong c\u00e1c k\u00ec thi quan tr\u1ecdng: H\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, th\u00ec h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3, thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">N\u1ebfu con \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 cha m\u1eb9 n\u00ean t\u00ecm cho con m\u1ed9t <strong>gia s\u01b0 v\u0103n<\/strong> d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0. Gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap con th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn con c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1edb, t\u0103ng v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_DIA_CHI_TIM_GIA_SU_DAY_VAN_UY_TIN_O_HA_NOI\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\">II &#8211; \u0110\u1ecaA CH\u1ec8 T\u00ccM GIA S\u01af D\u1ea0Y V\u0102N UY T\u00cdN \u1ede H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 uy t\u00edn, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i g\u1eedi g\u1eafm ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u cha m\u1eb9 hi\u1ec7n nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0 9 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u, tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p <strong>gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n v\u0103n<\/strong> gi\u1ecfi, c\u00f3 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0 H\u01a1n 300+ gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y v\u0103n gi\u1ecfi v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc kh\u1ed1i C t\u1eeb 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c <strong>gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n v\u0103n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0 Gia s\u01b0 v\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng TOP 1 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0: S\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0110H KHXH &amp; NV, \u0110H Lu\u1eadt&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0 C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 \u0111ang d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n V\u0103n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea5p 1,2,3 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. C\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 c\u00f3 kinh ngi\u1ec7m l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ngh\u1ec1, gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc sinh nh\u01b0: m\u1ea5t g\u1ed1c, ngh\u1ecbch, trung b\u00ecnh, \u00f4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, chuy\u00ean&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1093\" src=\"http:\/\/giasuhanoigioi.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/icon-trung-tam-gia-su.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"18\" height=\"16\" \/>\u00a0 Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng trung t\u00e2m uy t\u00edn s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, sinh vi\u00ean theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1571\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1571\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1571\