>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 3<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000 - 400.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, HS chuy\u00ean<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-22 from cache -->\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\">Xem th\u00eam:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">[B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1] <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\"><strong>H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0<\/strong><\/a> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i &#8211; M\u00f4n To\u00e1n, Anh, V\u0103n, Ho\u00e1, L\u00fd<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">TOP 3000+ <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\">gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh<\/a><\/strong> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u2013 T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 g\u1ea5p 5 l\u1ea7n<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_TU_VAN_NEN_LUA_CHON_GIA_SU_LA_SINH_VIEN_HAY_GIAO_VIEN\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>IV &#8211; T\u01af V\u1ea4N: N\u00caN L\u1ef0A CH\u1eccN GIA S\u01af L\u00c0 SINH VI\u00caN HAY GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em>N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn sinh vi\u00ean khi:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0N\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp con c\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng l\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0Con kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i v\u00ec c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0Con \u0111ang h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c l\u1edbp kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u1ea5p quan tr\u1ecdng<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1573\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1573\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1573\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-lua-chon-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-lua-chon-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-lua-chon-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-lua-chon-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/nen-lua-chon-gia-su-la-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1573\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><em>N\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean?<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong><em>N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean khi:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con m\u1ea5t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u0103n b\u1ea3n tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng. \u0110i\u1ec3m thi c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con l\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebfng, ham ch\u01a1i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666 \u0110\u00e3 h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u gia s\u01b0 sinh vi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con b\u1ea1n \u0111ang h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c l\u1edbp cu\u1ed1i c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 5, 9, 12<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666 Con b\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 thi l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi c\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1ea5p huy\u1ec7n, t\u1ec9nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"V_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_GIA_SU_BINH_MINH\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><b>V &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH MINH<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho h\u1ecdc sinh &amp; ph\u1ee5 huynh gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ CAM K\u1ebeT t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, t\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ H\u1ecdc th\u1eed 02 bu\u1ed5i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ Ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a con \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi 24\/7<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">+ T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin tuy\u1ec3n sinh, \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n\u2026v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u00ean, \u0110H \u2013 C\u0110.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>*****Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem th\u00eam gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n, Ti\u1ebfng Anh,&#8230;.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">[B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1] 500+ <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-500-gia-su-mon-toan-gioi-tu-lop-1-12-o-ha-noi\/\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/a> gi\u1ecfi \u2013 T\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1-12 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/\">GIA S\u01af TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC<\/a> CHO CON T\u1eea L\u1edaP 1-5<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>